{
  "stem": "10572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now after this memorable meeting in Berlin with Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hamilton and the letter that arrived with her confirmation of her original promise on the 6th of October, four weeks later-- after this first letter arrived-- a young Jewish boy by the name of Herschel Grynszpan went to the German embassy in Paris after learning that his mother was killed after being deported by the Nazis to Poland.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went in the German embassy and shot the first German he saw, Legation Secretary vom Rath.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew by this time that the Nazis wouldn't let an opportunity like that go by.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used this to the fullest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And out of this killing-- unfortunate killing, because vom Rath was on the list of the Gestapo as an anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Vom Rath died a couple of days afterwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew it was now our turn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- on the 9th of November, we got a registered letter from the mayor of our city telling us that in-- in retaliation for the conspiracy of international Jewry-- and this was a typical Nazi term-- that we were, as punishment-- that we had to liquidate all remaining business organizations within the next two weeks.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my father was out of town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He came back that night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he and I sat down and made plans how we could comply with this order.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after we had our meeting, I sat down at my desk and wrote a letter to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hamilton, telling her that by the time this letter would reach her, she would know what the crazy deed of a young boy did to all of us, not realizing of course, at that particular point, that by the time she got the letter, that my wording had much more weight than when I wrote it because of the-- what happened to us during the next hours and days and months.",
      "word_count": 71
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mailed the letter at midnight on the 9th of November.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't have a very good night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't get to sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at around 5 o'clock in the morning, there was a-- the doorbell rang.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a knock at the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked at my clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe anybody at 5 o'clock in the morning coming to our house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, get your father down here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to talk to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went upstairs in my parents' bedroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother had an ailing heart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't know how to prepare them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but nevertheless, I told them the Gestapo was downstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my parents came down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't do anything, didn't go through any-- didn't look for anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And only later on did we find out that they were particularly human in our case because in other incidents, they had gone into houses and smashed the libraries and tore down the chandeliers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nothing was touched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of the reasons was that one of the SS officers was the son-in-law of our next-door neighbor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think that he kept it under control.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he told us, nevertheless, that we should get dressed-- my father and I should get dressed-- and come with them to Gestapo headquarters for further interrogation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father came into my room and said, we're not coming back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Get dressed very warm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this time, his skepticism was justified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I listened to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I put on my ski boots and my ski sweater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And those warm clothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Maybe it saved my life after we got to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, we had no-- we had no idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing was both my father and I knew-- and maybe I should say this here-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] in the previous spring, one of our-- one of the good friends of my father, who was a lawyer, Catholic lawyer, had come to my father to say goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father looked at him and said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, I'm leaving Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Said, I cannot stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he told him that his law clerk had been on summer training in the SS and had been a guard in a concentration camp and had come back and told Franz [?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nilsen, ?] this lawyer, what he had seen, even though he was not supposed to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Franz [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nilsen ?] came to the conclusion that any country where this could happen, he didn't want to live in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father convinced him that he was pushing it a little bit too far and that he shouldn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
